title: [Ravine, Vulture's Nest]
description: Broken branches, thatches of dried grass, clods of dirt, and bits of feathers and dried flesh and bone from long-dead corpses make up the massive nest.  A crumbling outcropping of stone hangs directly overhead, blocking out the sun.

Broken branches, thatches of dried grass, clods of dirt, and bits of feathers and dried flesh and bone from long-dead corpses make up the massive nest.  A crumbling outcropping of stone hangs directly overhead, blocking any view of the stars above.
